title: Top 10 Parody Songs of Mintoo Dasgupta | Old Bengali Songs | Audio Jukebox
description:
This Jukebox presents 10 very popular parody of evergreen Hits of yesteryears sung by top most parody singer of Bengal Mintoo Dasgupta. These songs were released as his PUJA offerings and became superhits like originals in 60's to 80's. Listen and Enjoy!!! Do not forget to "Subscribe" to our channel.
